commit.message:
tm.texi: Add brackets around the return type of TARGET_SECONDARY_RELOAD.

2007-03-19  Andreas Krebbel  <krebbel1@de.ibm.com>

	* doc/tm.texi: Add brackets around the return type of
	TARGET_SECONDARY_RELOAD.
